postgresql installation:

for mac os x:
- go to https://postgresapp.com/
- install as said in all 3 instructions

after installation open the command line and enter these commands:
- sudo -u [YOUR USERNAME] createuser -SRdP modir
- enter the password in settings.py in databases section
- sudo -u soroush createdb --owner modir --template template0 -E UTF8 dollarial

no errors should raise in any step
